OL,3,CThe defiant pit community that united
OL,4,Cafter being 'destroyed'
OL,6,FShortly after its colliery closed in
OL,7,F1993, Grimethorpe was dubbed Britain's
OL,8,Fpoorest village.
OL,10,FTwelve years earlier, the census
OL,11,Frecorded that 44% of all workers in
OL,12,Fthe South Yorkshire village were
OL,13,Femployed in the pits.
OL,15,FMany of them walked out during the
OL,16,Fultimately futile strikes of 1984-5.
