OL,3,CThe defiant pit community that united
OL,4,Cafter being 'destroyed'
OL,6,FLike so many other working class
OL,7,Fcommunities, when the colliery closed,
OL,8,Fdepriving it of the industry on which
OL,9,Fit once relied, Grimethorpe entered a
OL,10,Fpredictable period of decline.
OL,12,FFor much of the 1990s unemployment was
OL,13,Fabove 50%. Crime spiralled. Housing
OL,14,Festates were over-run with drugs.
OL,16,FMillions of pounds of investment - and
OL,17,Fthe opening of factories and
OL,18,Fdistribution centres around the former
OL,19,Fpit site - followed.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
