OL,3,CThe defiant pit community that united
OL,4,Cafter being 'destroyed'
OL,6,FBut the legacy of the failed battle to
OL,7,Fsave the pits endures.
OL,9,FGrimethorpe still has fewer people in
OL,10,Fwork, more deprived households and
OL,11,Fmore people suffering ill-health than
OL,12,Fthe national average.
OL,14,FCllr Sir Steve Houghton, the leader of
OL,15,FBarnsley Council, said: "The job's not
OL,16,Fdone. Let's not sit here and say the
OL,17,Fproblems have been solved. There are
OL,18,Fstill significant challenges so we're
OL,19,Fnot complacent."
