OL,3,CThe defiant pit community that united
OL,4,Cafter being 'destroyed'
OL,6,FBut in adversity there were stories of
OL,7,Fgrit which shaped the attitudes of
OL,8,Ffamilies for generations. Julie
OL,9,FLindley was among the women who dug
OL,10,Fin, literally, to keep the home fires
OL,11,Fburning.
