OL,3,CThe defiant pit community that united
OL,4,Cafter being 'destroyed'
OL,6,FJulie, now 66, said: "Every day, seven
OL,7,Fdays a week, on (the) coal stack,
OL,8,Fthere were quite a few of us from
OL,9,FGrimethorpe. We used to go with a
OL,10,Fshovel and a riddle, sacks, I started
OL,11,Foff with just a pushbike, (pick up)
OL,12,Ftwo sacks of coal, pushed it home, and
OL,13,Fthen sometimes the police would come
OL,14,Fand shoo us off, not in a nice way,
OL,15,Fbut there you go.
OL,17,F"But (you) brush yourself off and
OL,18,Fstart again, and that's how it was for
OL,19,Fa year."
