OL,3,CThe defiant pit community that united
OL,4,Cafter being 'destroyed'
OL,6,FToday all that is left of Grimethorpe
OL,7,FColliery is its brass band, set up in
OL,8,F1917.
OL,10,FThe newly-formed junior band meets
OL,11,Fonce a week to create opportunities
OL,12,Ffor a new generation of players.
OL,14,FBand member, 11-year-old Amelia
OL,15,FCusworth, said being part of the band
OL,16,Fwas "amazing" and she enjoyed "the
OL,17,Fsocial side".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/12
