OL,3,CThe defiant pit community that united
OL,4,Cafter being 'destroyed'
OL,6,FFellow band member Rufus Raddings,
OL,7,Falso 11, plays the cornet and said
OL,8,Fbeing in the band had given him
OL,9,F"confidence".
OL,11,FBand manager Richard Windle said:
OL,12,F"Over the last couple of decades,
OL,13,Fmusic in schools has become more and
OL,14,Fmore challenging for those that come
OL,15,Ffrom more deprived areas. We don't
OL,16,Fthink it should be just those that can
OL,17,Fafford to have lessons that receive
OL,18,Flessons, so we're committed to
OL,19,Fproviding everything for free."
