OL,3,CThe defiant pit community that united
OL,4,Cafter being 'destroyed'
OL,6,FThe band's survival is symbolic of the
OL,7,Fcommunity's resilience.
OL,9,FDanny Gillespie, who worked in the pit
OL,10,Ffor than 30 years, said the government
OL,11,Fhad "destroyed" the village but it had
OL,12,Fbounced back "because of the community
OL,13,Fand the people".
OL,15,FHe said: "I wouldn't live anywhere
OL,16,Felse, I could go anywhere I wanted,
OL,17,Fbut I'd sooner live here."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/12
