OL,3,CThe defiant pit community that united
OL,4,Cafter being 'destroyed'
OL,6,FAlthough the events of the past have
OL,7,Fleft their scars, there remains hope
OL,8,Ffor the future and a new perspective
OL,9,Ffor many people living in Grimethorpe.
OL,11,FMr Gillespie said: "We're living
OL,12,Flonger. We wouldn't have lived this
OL,13,Flong, I'm 80 years old now. We
OL,14,Fwouldn't have lived this long if we'd
OL,15,Fhad to stop down that pit all that
OL,16,Ftime, but not only that, it saved
OL,17,Fyoung people having to go and work
OL,18,Fdown that horrible horrible pit.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/12
